These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, fanta, juice, soy-milk, sprite, tea
The people have 7 different hobbies: magic-tricks, woodworking, puzzles, skydiving, board-games, card-games, singing
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, cricket, golf, skateboarding, surfing, swimming
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, quad-bike, ship, subway, train, van
 1. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 3. the person driving the subway is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the person driving the van is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 8. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the van and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
 9. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
10. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is baseball is the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person drinking soy-milk is the person driving the bike##1
13. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
14. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person driving the quad-bike##1
15. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
16. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
17. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
18. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
19. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | sprite        | soy-milk | fanta      | juice     | 7up      | tea     |
